{"tid":800765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"M+博物館爛尾　新昌擔保人遭索3億","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:44:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0adbd3122e79aee2ee3ee37d5a7857e604bc94","tid":800765,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180831/20488682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F20488682&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64RxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=eba0d686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F20488682&h=cda0ba28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180831/20488682</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月31日 <br />\n<br />\nM+博物館爛尾　新昌擔保人遭索3億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180831/large/18828147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F18828147.jpg&h=4d3751ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nM+博物館早前因新昌陷財困被迫停工。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】捲入港鐵沙中綫土瓜灣站削短鋼筋醜聞、負責西九文化區「M+博物館」工程的總承建商新昌營造廠財困，本月中被西九文化區管理局終止合約。西九管理局日前入稟高等法院控告作為新昌擔保人的保險公司，對工程爛尾索償近3億元。<br />\n<br />\n西九管理局追數的入稟狀無寫明牽涉新昌營造廠，只稱按2015年10月的擔保書，被告美亞保險香港有限公司作為擔保人，拖欠局方2.97億元，局方本月中發信追討不果，遂興訟追究。西九管理局昨回覆查詢確認，美亞的擔保書是由新昌營造廠根據合約要求提供。管理局終止聘用新昌後，決定向美亞要求繳付擔保書金額。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母公司宣佈出售全部股份<br />\n<br />\n新昌財困醜聞不絕，令西九管理局上月罕有地直接向14家分判商支付工程費。過去一周，新昌先被積金局追討434萬元欠供強積金，以及遭工程公司入稟申請清盤，日前再有深圳水泥公司指新昌就洪水橋公屋項目訂購了1.1億元預製石屎，但欠443萬元尾數未付，入稟追討。<br />\n<br />\n母公司新昌集團控股（00404）昨公佈，計劃出售新昌營造廠全部股份，與中國成立、主要從事建築業務的公司簽訂無法律約束力的諒解備忘錄，買方同意提供6億元支持新昌營造廠營運，其中3億須於備忘錄日期起一星期內提供，餘款兩星期內提供。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA2037、2039/18<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣、伍嘉豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n馬會換屆　周永健接棒做主席"},{"pid":"58133b048823ece596fe31814b28b9c2c9006113","tid":800765,"uid":64858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人埋單"},{"pid":"5bacdefab4b436246c45cf407717525033d69b98","tid":800765,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"surety bond 威力"},{"pid":"206487957e9a684efa8ea09e7bd32e7790c0a229","tid":800765,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"想套殻走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e175d5631137f785be1adc0a4e0feca499b8bd","tid":800765,"uid":70357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bacdefab4b436246c45cf407717525033d69b98","tid":800765,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"surety bond 威力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"保險應該賺唔少，好少出大事"},{"pid":"b03038901bb964a184a87dab7beb2adeeb10138d","tid":800765,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"可能是最大贏家"},{"pid":"b515432f0a67c420b38f2e266a99f36f160d9172","tid":800765,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28e175d5631137f785be1adc0a4e0feca499b8bd","tid":800765,"uid":70357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bacdefab4b436246c45cf407717525033d69b98","tid":800765,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"surety bond 威力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"保險應該賺唔少，好少出大事"},"citedBy":0,"re